              ·fn
                fn ·ƒctx_66: ·ƒv_30 ·ƒctx_66, ·ƒsucc_3
                fn ·ƒv_36:
                  ·fn
                    fn ·ƒctx_68, ·ƒsucc_7, ·ƒfail_8, ·ƒv_6:
                      ·op_rngin ·ƒctx_68, (i8 0), (i8 10), fn ·ƒctx_70, ·ƒv_19:
